    <id>http://www.ahwkong.com/post/2013/04/17/p-48145048805</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>First, to install, follow the instrument here:</p>

<p><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/a/13718915/58129">http://stackoverflow.com/a/13718915/58129</a></p>

<p>You may then get a <code>Could not reserve enough space for object heap</code> exception. The following command line works for me:</p>

<p><code>sbt -J-Xms256m -J-Xmx512m</code></p>
]]></content>
